<section id="financial">
    <h2>Financial Empowerment Schemes</h2>
    <div class="category-intro">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Financial Empowerment" class="category-icon">
        <p>These schemes provide financial support, loans, and economic opportunities to help women achieve financial independence and grow their businesses.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Stand-Up India Loan Scheme" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Stand-Up India Loan Scheme</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>Facilitates bank loans between ₹10 lakh and ₹1 crore to at least one Scheduled Caste (SC) or Scheduled Tribe (ST) borrower and at least one woman borrower per bank branch for setting up a greenfield enterprise.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> SC/ST and/or women entrepreneurs aged 18+ years
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Loan Amount:</span> ₹10 lakh to ₹1 crore
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Repayment Period:</span> Up to 7 years with moratorium period up to 18 months
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Interest Rate:</span> Lowest applicable rate of the bank
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.standupmitra.in" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Apply Now</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: standupmitra.in</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-8d04cb21cd6c?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Pradhan Mantri MUDRA Yojana" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Pradhan Mantri MUDRA Yojana (PMMY)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>Provides loans up to ₹10 lakh to non-corporate, non-farm small/micro enterprises, with special focus on women entrepreneurs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Women entrepreneurs wanting to start or expand small businesses
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Loan Categories:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Shishu: Loans up to ₹50,000</li>
                    <li>Kishor: Loans from ₹50,001 to ₹5 lakh</li>
                    <li>Tarun: Loans from ₹5 lakh to ₹10 lakh</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Interest Rate:</span> As per bank's MUDRA loan rates (typically 10-12%)
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Collateral:</span> No collateral required for loans up to ₹10 lakh
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.mudra.org.in" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Apply Now</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: mudra.org.in</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521791055366-0d553872125f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="National Rural Livelihoods Mission" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">National Rural Livelihoods Mission (NRLM) Support</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>Aims to create efficient and effective institutional platforms for rural women, enabling them to increase household income through sustainable livelihood enhancements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Rural women, especially from BPL families
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Key Components:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Formation of women Self Help Groups (SHGs)</li>
                    <li>Financial inclusion and access to credit</li>
                    <li>Skill development and capacity building</li>
                    <li>Support for livelihood activities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Benefits:</span> Access to revolving fund, community investment fund, and bank credit
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://aajeevika.gov.in" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: aajeevika.gov.in</span>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="health">
    <h2>Health & Maternity Schemes</h2>
    <div class="category-intro">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579684385127-1ef15d508118?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Health & Maternity" class="category-icon">
        <p>These programs focus on women's health, maternal care, and ensuring access to quality healthcare services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517120026326-d87759a7b0dd?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Pradhan Mantri Matru Vandana Yojana" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Pradhan Mantri Matru Vandana Yojana (PMMVY)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>A maternity benefit program providing cash incentives for improved health and nutrition to pregnant and lactating mothers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Pregnant women and lactating mothers (excluding those in regular employment)
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Benefits:</span> ₹5,000 in three installments:
                <ul>
                    <li>₹1,000 on early registration of pregnancy</li>
                    <li>₹2,000 after six months of pregnancy on receiving at least one ante-natal check-up</li>
                    <li>₹2,000 after child birth is registered and the child has received first cycle of vaccinations</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Coverage:</span> For first live birth only
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wcd.nic.in/schemes/pradhan-mantri-matru-vandana-yojana" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Apply Now</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Portal: wcd.nic.in</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Ayushman Bharat" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Ayushman Bharat - Pradhan Mantri Jan Arogya Yojana (AB-PMJAY)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>Provides health coverage of ₹5 lakh per family per year for secondary and tertiary care hospitalization to over 10 crore poor and vulnerable families.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Families identified as per Socio-Economic Caste Census (SECC) data
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Coverage:</span> 1,393 medical procedures including maternity care
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Women-Specific Benefits:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>No cap on family size</li>
                    <li>All pre-existing conditions covered from day one</li>
                    <li>Cashless and paperless access to empaneled hospitals</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://pmjay.gov.in" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Check Eligibility</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: pmjay.gov.in</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581056771107-24ca5f033842?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Janani Suraksha Yojana" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Janani Suraksha Yojana (JSY)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>A safe motherhood intervention to reduce maternal and neonatal mortality by promoting institutional delivery among poor pregnant women.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Pregnant women from BPL families, aged 19+ years
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Benefits:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Rural areas: ₹1,400 for institutional delivery</li>
                    <li>Urban areas: ₹1,000 for institutional delivery</li>
                    <li>Additional ₹200 to ASHA worker for facilitating institutional delivery</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Additional Support:</span> Free delivery including C-section at public health facilities
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://nhm.gov.in/index1.php?lang=1&level=2&sublinkid=822&lid=218" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Portal: nhm.gov.in</span>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="education">
    <h2>Educational Empowerment Schemes</h2>
    <div class="category-intro">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523050854058-8df90110c9f1?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Educational Empowerment" class="category-icon">
        <p>Programs aimed at promoting girls' education, skill development, and long-term financial security through education.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524179091875-bf99a9a6af57?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Beti Bachao Beti Padhao" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Beti Bachao Beti Padhao (BBBP)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>A comprehensive program to address the declining Child Sex Ratio (CSR) and related issues of empowerment of women over a life-cycle continuum.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Key Components:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Prevent gender-biased sex selective elimination</li>
                    <li>Ensure survival & protection of the girl child</li>
                    <li>Ensure education and participation of the girl child</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Implementation:</span> Through mass communication campaign and multi-sectoral action
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Recent Initiatives:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Sukanya Samriddhi Yojana linkage</li>
                    <li>School enrollment drives for girls</li>
                    <li>Awareness programs on gender equality</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://wcd.nic.in/bbbp-schemes" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: wcd.nic.in</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Pradhan Mantri Kaushal Vikas Yojana" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Pradhan Mantri Kaushal Vikas Yojana (PMKVY) Training</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>Skill development initiative to enable Indian youth to take up industry-relevant skill training that will help them in securing a better livelihood.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Indian women aged 15-45 years
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Key Features:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Short-term training programs (150-300 hours)</li>
                    <li>Special focus on women-centric job roles</li>
                    <li>Training aligned to National Skill Qualification Framework</li>
                    <li>Placement assistance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Women-Specific Benefits:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Stipend of ₹500 per week during training</li>
                    <li>Special women-only batches available</li>
                    <li>Courses in beauty, healthcare, apparel, etc.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.pmkvyofficial.org" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Find Training Centers</a>
        <span class="official-link">Official Website: pmkvyofficial.org</span>
    </div>

    <div class="scheme-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579621970563-ebec7560ff3e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Sukanya Samriddhi Yojana" class="scheme-image">
        <h3 class="scheme-name">Sukanya Samriddhi Yojana (SSY)</h3>
        <div class="scheme-description">
            <p>A small deposit savings scheme for girl children that offers attractive interest rates and tax benefits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scheme-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Eligibility:</span> Girl child below 10 years of age
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Key Features:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Minimum deposit: ₹250 per year</li>
                    <li>Maximum deposit: ₹1.5 lakh per year</li>
                    <li>Current interest rate: 7.6% (FY 2023-24)</li>
                    <li>Account can be opened at post offices or authorized banks</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Tax Benefits:</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>Section 80C deduction for deposits</li>
                    <li>Tax-free interest</li>
                    <li>Tax-free maturity amount</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-title">Maturity:</span> Account matures when girl turns 21 (partial withdrawal allowed after 18 for education/marriage)
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.indiapost.gov.in" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Open Account</a>
        <span class="official-link">Available at Post Offices and Authorized Banks</span>
    </div>
</section>